{"data":[{"date":"15:47 31/07","title":"Everton chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/1/7/everton-chi-30-trieu-bang-mua-marcos-rojo.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Marcos Rojo c\u1ee7a MU, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Marcos Rojo\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 Marcos Rojo kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o M.U. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Marcos Rojo c\u1ee7a MU v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Marcos Rojo c\u1ee7a MU v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/18/Everton-muon-mua-Marcos-Rojo-cua-MU-voi-gia-cuc-soc-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Marcos Rojo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Mourinho \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n mua m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 nh\u1eafm Harry Maguire ho\u1eb7c Toby Alderweireld \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. M.U ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Marcos Rojo \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a M.U, n\u1ebfu Marcos Rojo ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Mirror, M.U s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Marcos Rojo, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-ngoai-hang-anh-chi-25-trieu-bang-mua-marcos-rojo-172-192177.html\" target=\"_blank\">Wolves mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Marcos Rojo</span>,\u00a0Watford, Everton v\u00e0 West Ham c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Everton chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Marcos Rojo</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Marcos Rojo c\u1ee7a MU, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Everton chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Everton chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/16/Everton-chi-30-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-MU-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Everton chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Marcos Rojo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Marco Silva mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, \u00f4ng nh\u1eafm ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a M.U nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Everton, Marcos Rojo s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi M.U, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i trung v\u1ec7 Marcos Rojo, Everton c\u00f2n nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia. Mina c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a M.U, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Maguire ho\u1eb7c Alderweireld.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1847","checkdouble":"192398"},{"date":"15:12 31/07","title":"Guardiola m\u1edf c\u1eeda cho sao tr\u1ebb Man City ra \u0111i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/guardiola-phat-bieu-ve-harrison.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jack Harrison ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Guardiola. HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Man City khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 gia nh\u1eadp Leeds United c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i Marcelo Bielsa.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Harrison t\u1edbi Leeds tu nghi\u1ec7p</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJack Harrison t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o t\u1ea1i hai h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a Liverpool v\u00e0 Man United. N\u0103m 14 tu\u1ed5i, anh theo gia \u0111\u00ecnh sang M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 kh\u1edfi nghi\u1ec7p \u1edf New York City, m\u1ed9t CLB c\u00f3 chung ch\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u00e0 t\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n City Football Group v\u1edbi Man City.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018, Harrison \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n giao cho Man City song l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho Middlesbrough m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Anh ra s\u00e2n 4 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harrison ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Guardiola v\u00e0 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi Leeds h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Harrison ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Guardiola v\u00e0 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi Leeds h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/guardiola-phat-bieu-ve-harrison.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Harrison t\u1edbi Leeds thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede \u0111\u1ee3t du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9, Harrison \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 b\u1eaft t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e0ng trai s\u1eafp tr\u00f2n 22 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3. M\u1edbi h\u00f4m qua, Harrison \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Leeds United \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Guardiola m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cho h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPep Guardiola th\u01b0\u1eddng chia s\u1ebb r\u1eb1ng HLV n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng Marcelo Bielsa c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ebfn tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u00d4ng tin r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Leeds c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Jack Harrison ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep Guardiola\" title=\"Pep Guardiola\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/pep-guardiola-khen-ngoi-hoc-tro-du-de-thua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Harrison ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Guardiola v\u00e0 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 kh\u00edch l\u1ec7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Pep Guardiola v\u1ec1 Marcelo Bielsa v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi kh\u00edch l\u1ec7\u201d, Harrison ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Guardiola tr\u00ean trang web ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Leeds. \u201cR\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Pep \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Bielsa. V\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u1eefu \u00edch cho t\u00f4i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. V\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i Leeds. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i th\u00eam ng\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Elland Road, cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-mua-kante-neu-mat-pjanic-vao-tay-man-city-172-191995.html\">V\u00ec Man City, Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Kante v\u00e0o tay Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cong-than-man-city-quyet-tam-dao-tau-khoi-ach-pep-guardiola-172-191855.html\">C\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n Man City quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea9u kh\u1ecfi \u00e1ch Pep Guardiola</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sau-mahrez-man-city-sap-co-them-bom-tan-100-trieu-euro-172-191834.html\">Sau Mahrez, Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f3 th\u00eam bom t\u1ea5n 100 tri\u1ec7u euro</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hart-muon-roi-man-city-de-cuu-van-su-nghiep-172-191782.html\">C\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-len-ke-hoach-chia-tay-sterling-172-191666.html\">Man City l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chia tay c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1846","checkdouble":"192399"},{"date":"16:32 31/07","title":"Tottenham nh\u1eadn b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng d\u00e0nh cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u01a1 b\u1eafp","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/tottenham-phai-mua-kondogbia-gia-70-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u00e1n b\u1edbt m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 danh s\u00e1ch 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Denis Suarez</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, 24 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Denis Suarez kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca. Ng\u00f4i sao Sinh n\u0103m 1994 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 18 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, trong \u0111\u00f3 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 4 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 500 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Chuyen-nhuong-Barca-2018-co-the-chia-tay-7-cau-thu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Denis Suarez</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, song thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Anh ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arthur, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Denis Suarez \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Denis Suarez n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 20 \u0111\u1ebfn 25 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Hi\u1ec7n Valencia v\u00e0 Sevilla \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ousmane Dembele</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh, 21 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca b\u1ecf ra 105 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Ousmane Dembele t\u1eeb Dortmund, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou song ch\u1ec9 \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Ng\u00f4i sao 21 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n sau 19 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf La Liga.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ousmane Dembele\" title=\"Ousmane Dembele\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/dembele.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ousmane Dembele</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Dembele thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Barca ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh. Sau khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Antoine Grizmann v\u00e0 Willian, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 42 tri\u1ec7u euro.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Ousmane Dembele b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ef1u sao Dortmund n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Hi\u1ec7n Chelsea \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Rafinha</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, 25 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRafinha kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Barca, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil th\u1eadm ch\u00ed b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y t\u1edbi Inter Milan theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rafinha\" title=\"Rafinha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/rafinha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rafinha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n gi\u1eefa Rafinha v\u00e0 Inter Milan c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro, trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi ch\u1ec9 ghi 2 b\u00e0n sau 17 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Serie A.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt, Inter \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t. Rafinha \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca, song t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Arsenal v\u00e0 Tottenham, Barca c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil n\u1ebfu thu v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 20 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Paco Alcacer</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, 24 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPaco Alcacer \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Luis Suarez, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n c\u00f3 17 l\u1ea7n \u1edf La Liga, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 8 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paco Alcacer\" title=\"Paco Alcacer\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/acaser.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Paco Alcacer</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 Suarez \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u b\u01b0\u1edbc sang s\u01b0\u1eddn d\u1ed1c b\u00ean kia c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, Barca c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay. Paco Alcacer kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou t\u00ednh b\u00e1n anh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t Paco Alcacer, Barc c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Hi\u1ec7n Valencia \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Bilbao c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Andre Gomes</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, 25 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Andre Gomes kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Ernesto Valverde s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 6 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf La Liga, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Andre Gomes\" title=\"Andre Gomes\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/gomes.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Andre Gomes</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2016, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111ang g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Andre Gomes c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Hi\u1ec7n anh \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/arsenal-bat-ngo-muon-rut-ruot-barca-172-190353.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Andre Gomes</span>, Tottenham v\u00e0 M.U c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Gomes n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 30 tri\u1ec7u euro, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Aleix Vidal<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i, 28 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAleix Vidal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca, song m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a anh kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u00f3 4 l\u1ea7n \u1edf La Liga, anh hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Barca.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Aleix Vidal\" title=\"Aleix Vidal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/vidal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Aleix Vidal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSergi Roberto v\u00e0 Nelson Semedo c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Aleix Vidal g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n. Barca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch thanh l\u00fd c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 15 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Inter Milan l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Aleix Vidal, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Thomas Vermaelen</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7, 33 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Thomas Vermaelen ra s\u00e2n 14 l\u1ea7n \u1edf La Liga v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 1000 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, anh l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng cho Umtiti v\u00e0 Pique. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Arsenal s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thomas Vermaelen\" title=\"Thomas Vermaelen\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/vemar.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Thomas Vermaelen</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBarca \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Clement Lenglet, trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u1edf World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Barca \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trung v\u1ec7, HLV Ernesto Valverde kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. Theo Sport, c\u1ef1u sao Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch thanh l\u00fd \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Crystal Palace v\u00e0 Watford \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Vermaelen tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1845","checkdouble":"192400"},{"date":"16:43 31/07","title":"Antonio Conte: Hai n\u0103m n\u1ebfm tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee7 H\u1ec9 N\u1ed9 \u00c1i \u1ed0 c\u00f9ng Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/antonio-conte-hai-nam-nem-trai-du-hi-no-ai-o-cung-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1c \u0111\u1eddi HLV Chelsea, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 sau 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean thu\u1ed9c nhi\u1ec7m k\u00ec m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Mourinho, h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i trong ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a CLB. Mourinho, Scolari, Villas-Boas v\u00e0 Conte. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1eddi Chelsea theo m\u1ed9t \u201ck\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n\u201d ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n gi\u1ed1ng nhau: t\u1eeb b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi BL\u0110, \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Wembley t\u1ed1i 19/5, Chung k\u1ebft c\u00fap FA, Chelsea \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Manchester United 1-0 v\u1edbi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t 11m c\u1ee7a Eden Hazard. B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p Antonio Conte \u0111\u00e3 \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ea7y c\u1ea3m x\u00fac, v\u1edbi n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi t\u01b0\u01a1i r\u00f3i khi n\u00e2ng cao danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn th\u1ee9 2 \u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f9ng Chelsea, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng The Blues.</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Antonio Conte: Hai nam nem trai du Hi No Ai O cung Chelsea1\" title=\"Antonio Conte: Hai n\u0103m n\u1ebfm tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee7 H\u1ec9 N\u1ed9 \u00c1i \u1ed0 c\u00f9ng Chelsea1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/co.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Antonio Conte: Hai n\u0103m n\u1ebfm tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee7 H\u1ec9 N\u1ed9 \u00c1i \u1ed0 c\u00f9ng Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00e0y 13/7, t\u1ee9c 25 ng\u00e0y sau khi c\u00f9ng Chelsea v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap FA, Conte ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb&nbsp; BL\u0110 The Blues sa th\u1ea3i, k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u1ed9t tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00e9o d\u00e0i v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 2 n\u0103m nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1eafc m\u00e0u t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge. Gi\u1edd Conte \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00ean l\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Gi\u1edd The Blues \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh HLV m\u1edbi, m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia kh\u00e1c - Maurizio Sarri. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn, c\u00e1c True Blues s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn k\u00ed \u1ee9c n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 Conte?&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t Conte h\u1eebng h\u1ef1c t\u00ednh chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng pitch? M\u1ed9t Conte t\u00e0i ba h\u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi khi \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh 3-4-3 (c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c bi\u1ebfn th\u1ec3 3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7) \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Chelsea v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nh\u1eefng tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i trong m\u00f9a \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn chu\u1ed7i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League 2016/17? M\u1ed9t Conte &ldquo;\u0111\u1ed9c t\u00e0i&rdquo; qua tin nh\u1eafn&hellip; y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Diego Costa t\u00ecm CLB kh\u00e1c. M\u1ed9t Conte sa l\u1ea7y trong cu\u1ed9c kh\u1ea9u chi\u1ebfn cay nghi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Stamford Bridge &ndash; Jose Mourinho. Hay m\u1ed9t Conte c\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed9c trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Chelsea?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 Conte trong tim c\u00e1c C\u0110V Chelsea c\u00f3 l\u00e0&hellip; Conte n\u00e0o th\u00ec n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh: Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia hay chia tay \u00f4ng, h\u1eb3n \u0111a s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c True Bules s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn v\u1ebf th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t. B\u1edfi h\u1ecd hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Chelsea th\u1eddi Roman Abramovich ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd n\u1eb1m \u1edf v\u1ecb t\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Conte \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt &ldquo;Conte&rdquo; nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. V\u00e0 sau Conte ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u &ldquo;Conte&rdquo; n\u1eefa. S\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf HLV \u1edf Stamford Bridge l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 qu\u00e1 xa x\u1ec9!<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea sa thai HLV Antonio Conte truoc them mua giai moi.\" title=\"Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/Thuc-hu-chuyen-Antonio-Conte-dan-dat-AC-Milan-thay-Gattuso-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau Conte, Sarri l\u00e0 HLV th\u1ee9 4 c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong v\u00f2ng 5 n\u0103m qua. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Conte b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 12 l\u01b0\u1ee3t HLV d\u1eabn d\u1eaft The Blues trong tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Abramovich, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ch\u1eefa ch\u00e1y v\u00e0i tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0 Ray Wilkins hay Steve Holland. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng hay vi\u1ec7c m\u1ea5t ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BL\u0110 Chelsea s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 sa th\u1ea3i, \u0111\u1ec3 chia tay HLV m\u00e0 h\u1ecd t\u1eebng &ldquo;tr\u1ea3i th\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ecf&rdquo; \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Stamford Bridge. Nh\u01b0 Conte!<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n b\u1ec1 n\u1ed5i. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n s\u00e2u xa lu\u00f4n b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng &ndash; m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn gi\u1eefa HLV Chelsea v\u00e0 Ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB. T\u1ec9 ph\u00fa Abramovich l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m thay \u0111\u1ed5i to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Chelsea th\u1eddi hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, bi\u1ebfn The Blues t\u1eeb ch\u1ed7 l\u00e0 1 CLB h\u1ea1ng kh\u00e1 nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 90 c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf k\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00e0nh 1 trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Premier League v\u00e0 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c t\u1eeb 2003. Nh\u01b0ng Abramovich c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 v\u0103n h\u00f3a d\u1ecb bi\u1ec7t Stamford Bridge khi\u1ebfn The Blues kh\u00e1c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng CLB h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Anh nh\u01b0 United, Liverpool hay Arsenal. M\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 v\u0103n h\u00f3a coi HLV \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m thu\u00ea cho Ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c \u0111\u1eddi HLV Chelsea, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 sau 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean thu\u1ed9c nhi\u1ec7m k\u00ec m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Mourinho, h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i trong ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a CLB. Mourinho, Scolari, Villas-Boas v\u00e0 Conte. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1eddi Chelsea theo m\u1ed9t &ldquo;k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n&rdquo; ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n gi\u1ed1ng nhau: t\u1eeb b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi BL\u0110, \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea thay conte sarri\" title=\"Chelsea thay conte sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/goc-nhin-chelsea-quyet-dinh-thay-the-conte-bang-sarri.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Chelsea thay Conte b\u1eb1ng HLV Sarri</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u00f3 t\u1ef1a \u0111\u1ec1 &ldquo;C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n ph\u00eda sau \u0110\u1ec9nh cao v\u00e0 V\u1ef1c s\u00e2u c\u1ee7a Conte \u1edf Chelsea&rdquo; \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i tr\u00ean Express h\u00f4m 13/6 &ndash; \u0111\u00fang 1 th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i, nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Simon Johnson vi\u1ebft: &ldquo;C\u00e1ch v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Chelsea kh\u00e1c \u0111a s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea1i Anh. Conte bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi v\u1ec1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y H\u00e8 2016. Tuy nhi\u00ean, sau khi gi\u00fap Chelsea \u0111\u0103ng quang Premier Laegue 2016/17 trong ho\u00e0nh c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t t\u1eeb CLB \u1edf c\u00e1c h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Conte tin r\u1eb1ng gi\u1edd \u00f4ng ta \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trong vi\u1ec7c mua b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a H\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n CLB. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Conte \u0111\u00e3 sai. Ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap v\u1ecb th\u1ebf \u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Conte v\u1edbi BL\u0110 The Blues \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng. Conte th\u1ef1c ra \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ee1 m\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb 1 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u1ec9 1 th\u00e1ng sau khi \u0111\u01b0a Chelsea l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch&rdquo;.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ph\u1ea3n th\u1ea7y&rdquo;, &ldquo;C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 gh\u1ebf HLV&rdquo;, ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. C\u1ee9 m\u1ed7i khi Chelsea c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 HLV c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00e2m nguy, truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 ph\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf c\u00e1c fan b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng t\u1eeb ng\u1eef nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 The Blues. \u0110\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 th\u1eadt, ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft. Nh\u01b0ng k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 c\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf th\u00ec nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n s\u1ed1 1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao tri\u1ec7u ph\u00fa c\u1ee7a Chelsea m\u00e0 l\u00e0 b\u1edfi BL\u0110 The Blues \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 ti\u1ec1n l\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb7t HLV \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ed1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00f3m c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n trong \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111a s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p. Nh\u01b0 bao \u0111\u1eddi HLV Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Conte c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u1ea5y trong h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Antonio Conte trong tran Chelsea 1-0 MU chung ket FA Cup 2017/18\" title=\"Antonio Conte trong tr\u1eadn Chelsea 1-0 MU chung k\u1ebft FA Cup 2017/18\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Zinedine-Zidane-tu-chuc-HLV-truong-cua-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Antonio Conte trong tr\u1eadn Chelsea 1-0 MU chung k\u1ebft FA Cup 2017/18</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Diego Costa ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Conte kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfc l\u1eddi sau v\u1ee5 l\u00f9m x\u00f9m &ldquo;tin nh\u1eafn cho ngh\u1ec9&rdquo; h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, Willian d\u00f9ng c\u00fap che m\u1eb7t Conte trong m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i r\u1ed9ng kh\u1eafp tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a. Courtois, trong khi \u0111\u00f3, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng Sarri gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea t\u1eeb cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 6 d\u00f9 Conte&ndash; tr\u00ean danh ngh\u0129a v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf - v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng The Blues. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u00f3m d\u1ecb bi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 Mario Balotelli hay Hatem Ben Arfa, m\u1ea5y khi d\u00e1m th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng b\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u00f3ng Ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB? \u0110\u1eddi Conte c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed t\u1ec7 b\u1ea1c \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady tr\u00ean t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t HLV, t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb thu\u00ea \u00f4ng v\u00e0 t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00f4m nay Conte \u0111\u00f3n sinh nh\u1eadt tu\u1ed5i 49 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i r\u1ea5t xa Chelsea, sau 2 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7y b\u00e3o t\u00e1p \u1edf Stamford Bridge. V\u00e0 bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t Sarri \u1edf v\u00e0o ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh nh\u01b0 Conte hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i? Hi v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng bi \u0111\u00e1t \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf&hellip;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>ELFLACO (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1844","checkdouble":"192401"},{"date":"17:24 31/07","title":"\u0110\u1ea1i gia NHA xem Lewandowski l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/28/chelsea-muon-mua-lewandowski-cua-bayern.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Lewandowski c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich. HLV Maurizio Sarri trong n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ba Lan nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea \u0111\u01b0a Lewandowski v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ban \u0111\u1ea7u, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Chelsea l\u00e0 Gonzalo Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina l\u1ea1i \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1edbi AC Milan v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 t\u1edd Daily Star c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Lewandowski c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ba Lan \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 Bundesliga ngay trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Lewandowski c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Lewandowski c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Chelsea-muon-mua-Lewandowski-cua-Bayern-Munich-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri c\u1ee7a Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Lewandowski</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n Chelsea, h\u1ecd \u0111ang kh\u00e1t m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Alvaro Morata g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 sau 1 n\u0103m t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge trong khi Olivier Giroud kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri. The Blues \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Bayern b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bayern c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Bayern Munich ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay v\u1edbi Lewandowski. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Dortmund v\u1edbi h\u1ecd c\u00f2n t\u1edbi t\u1eadn 4 n\u0103m m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n. Trong 126 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 qua, Lewandowski ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi 106 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Lewandowski\" title=\"tien dao Lewandowski\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/28/chelsea-muon-mua-lewandowski-cua-bayern.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Bayern c\u1ed1 gi\u1eef Lewandowski \u1edf l\u1ea1i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Premier League ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 9 ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n. Chelsea \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV Niko Kovac c\u1ee7a Bayern m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef Lewandowski c\u1ee7a Bayern. \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi CLB, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra \u0111i\u201d, Kovac n\u00f3i. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cRobert mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ec7n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y c\u00e0ng l\u00e2u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f9ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh t\u1ef1u t\u1ea1i Bundesliga, \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-chelsea-hot-nhat-ngay-3107-172-192406.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 31/07</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ly-do-khien-real-van-chua-the-cong-bo-bom-tan-courtois-172-192377.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Real v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 bom t\u1ea5n Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/willian-chinh-thuc-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-mu-va-real-madrid-172-192368.html\">Willian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho MU v\u00e0 Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/leicester-muon-mua-lai-drinkwater-172-192356.html\">Leicester mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u Drinkwater kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c Stamford Bridge</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chap-nhan-chi-65-trieu-bang-mua-pulisic-172-192340.html\">Chelsea ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua sao Dortmund</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1843","checkdouble":"192403"},{"date":"17:01 31/07","title":"7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/7-cau-thu-co-the-roi-barca-o-he-2018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u00e1n b\u1edbt m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 danh s\u00e1ch 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Denis Suarez</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, 24 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Denis Suarez kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca. Ng\u00f4i sao Sinh n\u0103m 1994 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 18 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, trong \u0111\u00f3 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 4 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 500 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Chuyen-nhuong-Barca-2018-co-the-chia-tay-7-cau-thu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Denis Suarez</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, song thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Anh ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arthur, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Denis Suarez \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Denis Suarez n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 20 \u0111\u1ebfn 25 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Hi\u1ec7n Valencia v\u00e0 Sevilla \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ousmane Dembele</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh, 21 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca b\u1ecf ra 105 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Ousmane Dembele t\u1eeb Dortmund, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou song ch\u1ec9 \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Ng\u00f4i sao 21 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n sau 19 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf La Liga.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ousmane Dembele\" title=\"Ousmane Dembele\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/dembele.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ousmane Dembele</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Dembele thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Barca ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh. Sau khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Antoine Grizmann v\u00e0 Willian, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 42 tri\u1ec7u euro.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Ousmane Dembele b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ef1u sao Dortmund n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Hi\u1ec7n Chelsea \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Rafinha</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, 25 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRafinha kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Barca, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil th\u1eadm ch\u00ed b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y t\u1edbi Inter Milan theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rafinha\" title=\"Rafinha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/rafinha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rafinha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n gi\u1eefa Rafinha v\u00e0 Inter Milan c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro, trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi ch\u1ec9 ghi 2 b\u00e0n sau 17 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Serie A.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt, Inter \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t. Rafinha \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca, song t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Arsenal v\u00e0 Tottenham, Barca c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil n\u1ebfu thu v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 20 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Paco Alcacer</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, 24 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPaco Alcacer \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Luis Suarez, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n c\u00f3 17 l\u1ea7n \u1edf La Liga, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 8 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paco Alcacer\" title=\"Paco Alcacer\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/acaser.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Paco Alcacer</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 Suarez \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u b\u01b0\u1edbc sang s\u01b0\u1eddn d\u1ed1c b\u00ean kia c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, Barca c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay. Paco Alcacer kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou t\u00ednh b\u00e1n anh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t Paco Alcacer, Barc c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Hi\u1ec7n Valencia \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Bilbao c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Andre Gomes</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, 25 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Andre Gomes kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Ernesto Valverde s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 6 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf La Liga, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Andre Gomes\" title=\"Andre Gomes\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/gomes.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Andre Gomes</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2016, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111ang g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Andre Gomes c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Hi\u1ec7n anh \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/arsenal-bat-ngo-muon-rut-ruot-barca-172-190353.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Andre Gomes</span>, Tottenham v\u00e0 M.U c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Gomes n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 30 tri\u1ec7u euro, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Aleix Vidal<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i, 28 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAleix Vidal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca, song m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a anh kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u00f3 4 l\u1ea7n \u1edf La Liga, anh hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Barca.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Aleix Vidal\" title=\"Aleix Vidal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/vidal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Aleix Vidal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSergi Roberto v\u00e0 Nelson Semedo c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Aleix Vidal g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n. Barca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch thanh l\u00fd c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 15 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Inter Milan l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Aleix Vidal, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Thomas Vermaelen</h2>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7, 33 tu\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Thomas Vermaelen ra s\u00e2n 14 l\u1ea7n \u1edf La Liga v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 1000 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, anh l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng cho Umtiti v\u00e0 Pique. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Arsenal s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thomas Vermaelen\" title=\"Thomas Vermaelen\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/vemar.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Thomas Vermaelen</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBarca \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Clement Lenglet, trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u1edf World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Barca \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trung v\u1ec7, HLV Ernesto Valverde kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. Theo Sport, c\u1ef1u sao Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch thanh l\u00fd \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Crystal Palace v\u00e0 Watford \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Vermaelen tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1842","checkdouble":"192405"},{"date":"17:14 31/07","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 31/07","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/chuyen-nhuong-chelsea-hot-nhat-ngay-3107.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a The Blues \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 31/07.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Lewandowski&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 3107 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 3107 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/5/Chuyen-nhuong-Chelsea-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-3107-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1eadm mua Lewandowski</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSong song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Gonzalo Higuain t\u1eeb Juventus, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Robert Lewandowski. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Bayern Munich \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Willian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho MU v\u00e0 Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Willian n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Chelsea v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Leicester mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u Drinkwater kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c Stamford Bridge</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLeicester mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Danny Drinkwater r\u1eddi Chelsea, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua l\u1ea1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua sao Dortmund</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Christian Pulisic c\u1ee7a Dortmund trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Eden Hazard ho\u1eb7c Willian ra \u0111i, The Blues ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng cho Real</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Thibaut Courtois v\u00e0 Willian. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1ed1t t\u1eeb ph\u00eda K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea th\u1eeba n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ee5c, c\u00e2u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ramsey\" title=\"Ramsey\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/Chelsea-muon-so-huu-ngoi-sao-Aaron-Ramsey-cua-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ramsey</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Ramsey c\u1ee7a Arsenal. Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u1eefa l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n trong khi HLV Maurizio Sarri c\u1ee7a The Blues l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t y\u00eau th\u00edch t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Giroud n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf Chelsea?</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Olivier Giroud r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed thay v\u00ec ra \u0111i t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Bakayoko ch\u1ec9 r\u1eddi Chelsea n\u1ebfu....</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tiemoue Bakayoko r\u1eddi Chelsea n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Man Utd v\u00e0 Chelsea nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 h\u00e0ng hot World Cup</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Claude Puel kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Leicester City s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kasper Schmeichel v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bailey cua Leverkusen\" title=\"Bailey cua Leverkusen\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/Vuot-mat-Chelsea,-Roma-muon-mua-Leon-Bailey--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Roma c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Bailey&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Roma mu\u1ed1n mua Leon Bailey c\u1ee7a Bayer Leverkusen, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 20 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>David Luiz mong mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea, ph\u00f2 t\u00e1 Sarri</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 David Luiz kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh v\u1eabn h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1841","checkdouble":"192406"},{"date":"17:56 31/07","title":"N\u00f3ng: Gonzalo Higuain \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd r\u1eddi Juventus h\u00e8 n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/23/higuain-dong-y-toi-milan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tin kh\u00f4ng vui v\u1ebb g\u00ec cho Chelsea: Gonzalo Higuain \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd r\u1eddi Juventus \u0111\u1ebfn AC Milan. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina ch\u01a1i cho Rossoneri d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 n\u0103m v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp n\u0103m sau.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Higuain ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi Milan</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo, h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Juventus tr\u1edf n\u00ean ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i. Ch\u00ednh t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Giuseppe Marotta c\u1ee7a Bianconeri \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Chelsea, Milan quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 31.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri c\u1ee7a Chelsea mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 v\u1edbi Higuain nh\u01b0 khi c\u00f2n \u1edf Napoli. Tuy nhi\u00ean, The Blues mu\u1ed1n thanh l\u00fd c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i Alvaro Morata v\u00e0 Olivier Giroud r\u1ed3i m\u1edbi ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Juventus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gonzalo Higuain \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd r\u1eddi Juventus \u0111\u1ebfn AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gonzalo Higuain \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd r\u1eddi Juventus \u0111\u1ebfn AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Gonzalo-Higuain-dong-y-roi-Juventus-den-AC-Milan-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Higuain v\u00e0 Bonucci s\u1eafp ho\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00e2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y, Milan \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn t\u1edbi Juventus. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Higuain trong 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 16 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 32,1 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m sau. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, Milan \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 Leonardo Bonucci tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi Mattia Caldara di chuy\u1ec3n theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i. Theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Higuain \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd r\u1eddi Juventus \u0111\u1ebfn Milan v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tin x\u1ea5u cho Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 d\u0129 nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 tin d\u1eef v\u1edbi HLV Sarri v\u00e0 Chelsea. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia r\u1ea5t m\u1ebfn m\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Higuain v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. Sarri t\u1eebng b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c anh t\u1edbi Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Higuain\" title=\"Higuain\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/14/Nhung-thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-tran-Juventus-2-2-Tottenham-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafm m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c thay Higuain</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ph\u00eda Milan \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t nh\u1ea1y b\u00e9n trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Khi m\u00e0 Juventus s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Milan, Chelsea bu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng ch\u00fa \u00fd. H\u1ecd d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Robert Lewandowski c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng trung phong l\u00e0 Olivier Giroud v\u00e0 Alvaro Morata. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Giroud \u0111ang trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra s\u00e2n. G\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Morata s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Chelsea \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Community Shield v\u1edbi Man City v\u00e0 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League v\u1edbi Huddersfield. <br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-chelsea-hot-nhat-ngay-3107-172-192406.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 31/07</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-mua-lewandowski-cua-bayern-172-192403.html\">\u0110\u1ea1i gia NHA xem Lewandowski l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/willian-chinh-thuc-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-mu-va-real-madrid-172-192368.html\">Willian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho MU v\u00e0 Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chap-nhan-chi-65-trieu-bang-mua-pulisic-172-192340.html\">Chelsea ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua sao Dortmund</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-mua-ramsey-va-vecino-172-192315.html\">Chelsea th\u1eeba n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ee5c, c\u00e2u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Arsenal</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1840","checkdouble":"192414"},{"date":"17:46 31/07","title":"3 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 thay Mourinho d\u1eabn d\u1eaft MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/3-ung-vien-sang-gia-thay-mourinho-dan-dat-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111ang lung lay d\u1eef d\u1ed9i khi \u00f4ng c\u00f4ng khai b\u00e0y t\u1ecf th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o MU. Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang sa s\u00fat th\u1eadm t\u1ec7. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean m\u00e0 Man United c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi thay th\u1ebf n\u1ebfu sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</h2><h2>Zinedine Zidane\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 thay Mourinho d\u1eabn d\u1eaft MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 thay Mourinho d\u1eabn d\u1eaft MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/3-ung-vien-sang-gia-thay-Mourinho-dan-dat-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u1edf Man United c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Zidane</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Zidane \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u1ecb s\u1ed1c khi r\u1eddi Real Madrid sau khi gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi tin r\u1eb1ng Zidane chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb n\u1eafm ch\u1ee9c v\u1ee5 HLV tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p sau World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, Didier Deschamps g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2020. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Zidane \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 Zidane, ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gh\u1ebf HLV tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn ng\u1ee7i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ngo\u00e0i t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng HLV v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t m\u1ecdi th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i, Zidane c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMan United c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng cho Zidane. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1ef1c d\u1eady h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i gia h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. N\u1ebfu Mourinho ra \u0111i, Zidane s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i. C\u00e1ch hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Zidane th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c xa so v\u1edbi Mourinho v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t lu\u1ed3ng gi\u00f3 m\u1edbi cho Man United.</div>\r\n<h2>Laurent Blanc\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG sa thai HLV Blanc\" title=\"PSG sa th\u1ea3i HLV Blanc\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/6/24/cuu-trung-ve-mu-lam-le-chiem-ghe-cua-mourinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Blanc c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m d\u1eabn d\u1eaft nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Blanc \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi vai tr\u00f2 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 n\u0103m nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi cho Man United n\u1ebfu Mourinho ra \u0111i. C\u1ef1u HLV Paris Saint-Germain t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i \u1edf Old Trafford t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2001 \u0111\u1ebfn 2003 v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Blanc t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sir Alex Ferguson \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eed ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV c\u1ee7a Man United. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf t\u1eebng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Blanc n\u0103m 2010. Nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 khi Sir Alex gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 n\u0103m 2013, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Paris.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, Blanc \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 n\u0103m d\u1eabn d\u1eaft PSG kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. \u00d4ng \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi 2 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ligue 1 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League 3 l\u1ea7n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. Nh\u01b0ng Blanc \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi PSG n\u0103m 2016 v\u00e0 k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Blanc c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Maurizio Sarri. Nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 52 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Blanc l\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t c\u00e1c c\u00e1 t\u00ednh m\u1ea1nh. Vi\u1ec7c Blanc c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb c\u0169ng m\u1edf ra m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u00e0 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<h2>Antonio Conte\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Conte\" title=\"Conte\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/174427-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Conte c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Conte \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 \u00edt l\u00e2u sau khi t\u1eadp trung tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd c\u00f2n \u0111ang \u1ea5p \u1ee7 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch kh\u1edfi ki\u1ec7n Chelsea v\u00ec ch\u1eadm tr\u1ec5 trong vi\u1ec7c sa th\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c m\u1edbi \u01b0ng \u00fd, qua \u0111\u00f3 thi\u1ec7t h\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 kinh t\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nConte \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c AC Milan trao m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 6 tri\u1ec7u euro/n\u0103m. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i c\u1ee7a Conte v\u1edbi Chelsea l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung t\u00ecm vi\u1ec7c m\u1edbi. Ph\u00eda Rossoneri nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t vi\u1ec7c quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd sau khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Serie A kh\u1edfi tranh ng\u00e0y 19/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Conte v\u1eabn th\u1ea5t nghi\u1ec7p sau khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u1edfi tranh th\u00ec \u00f4ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 MU c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc thay Mourinho. C\u1ef1u HLV Juventus v\u00e0 Chelsea c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m d\u1eabn d\u1eaft nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a Conte v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb v\u1edbi Man United. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, l\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Conte th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Sir Alex Ferguson. C\u00e1ch qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Conte ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 \u00f4ng lu\u00f4n h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn chung, vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Conte ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f4ng C\u0110V c\u1ee7a Man United \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu Mourinho ra \u0111i, Conte s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 l\u00e2u v\u1ec1 d\u00e0i cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nhan-dinh-mu-vs-real-madrid-07h05-ngay-18-icc-2018-184-192407.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Real Madrid 07h05 ng\u00e0y 1/8 (ICC 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-cam-doan-mu-se-co-them-tan-binh-172-192396.html\">Mourinho cam \u0111oan MU s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1839","checkdouble":"192415"},{"date":"17:53 31/07","title":"C\u0110V \u0110\u1ee9c bi\u1ec3u t\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng c\u1edd Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Ozil","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/31/cdv-duc-bieu-tinh-bang-co-tho-nhi-ky-de-ung-ho-ozil.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng ra \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Arsenal, theo phong tr\u00e0o T\u00f4i l\u00e0 Ozil.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMesut Ozil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c C\u0110V b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00e0y Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt v\u1eeba qua, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u fan h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ee5 t\u1eadp \u1edf Berlin, th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba cay \u0111\u1eafng n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay \u0110T sau nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u1ec1 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ozil cho r\u1eb1ng, anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd quay l\u1ea1i \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, ch\u1eebng n\u00e0o n\u1ea1n ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t s\u1eafc t\u1ed9c v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng C\u0110V n\u00e0y t\u1eadp trung b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n Axel Springer t\u1ea1i Berlin, gi\u01a1 cao nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m bi\u1ec3n hi\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng d\u00f2ng ch\u1eef &ldquo;Ich bin Ozil&rdquo; (ti\u1ebfng \u0110\u1ee9c: T\u00f4i l\u00e0 Ozil). Ngay c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee1i li\u1ec1m v\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao &ndash; bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho l\u00e1 c\u1edd Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u00e2n \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1eadp phong tr\u00e0o T\u00f4i l\u00e0 Ozil \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"D\u00e2n \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1eadp phong tr\u00e0o T\u00f4i l\u00e0 Ozil \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/ozil.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u0110V \u0110\u1ee9c bi\u1ec3u t\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng l\u00e1 c\u1edd Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p nh\u1eafm th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng quan ch\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c, \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Reinhard Grindel. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ozil tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 cay \u0111\u1eafng th\u1ed1t l\u00ean r\u1eb1ng: &ldquo;V\u1edbi Grindel v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u00f4ng ta, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c khi \u0110T gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, v\u00e0 l\u00e0 th\u1eb1ng nh\u1eadp c\u01b0 g\u1ed1c Th\u1ed5 khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i, anh \u0111\u00e3 x\u00f3a d\u00f2ng m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 &ldquo;C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u1ee9c&rdquo; tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i, ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i l\u1eddi gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Arsenal. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n \u0110\u1ee9c, h\u1ecd mong r\u1eb1ng phong tr\u00e0o T\u00f4i l\u00e0 Ozil s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn L\u0110B\u0110 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1eadp c\u01b0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u00e0o hoa n\u00e0y, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ec3n bi\u1ebfn t\u00edch c\u1ef1c cho nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1eadp c\u01b0 ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u00e2n \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1eadp phong tr\u00e0o T\u00f4i l\u00e0 Ozil \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham gia phong tr\u00e0o \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Ozil, ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i n\u1ea1n ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t s\u1eafc t\u1ed9c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/ozi1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham gia phong tr\u00e0o \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Ozil, ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i n\u1ea1n ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t s\u1eafc t\u1ed9c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u00e2n \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1eadp phong tr\u00e0o T\u00f4i l\u00e0 Ozil \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Kh\u1ea9u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a phong tr\u00e0o T\u00f4i l\u00e0 Ozil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/ozi12.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u1ea9u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a phong tr\u00e0o T\u00f4i l\u00e0 Ozil</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/noi-oan-cua-mesut-ozil-dinh-kien-ve-thai-do-184-192145.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/Ozil-bi-phan-biet-chung-toc-Hai-trai-tim-va-duc-hanh-o-bong-da-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/noi-oan-cua-mesut-ozil-dinh-kien-ve-thai-do-184-192145.html\">N\u1ed7i oan c\u1ee7a Mesut Ozil: \u0110\u1ecbnh ki\u1ebfn v\u1ec1 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9</span><br>\r\nCh\u00ednh nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ecbnh ki\u1ebfn v\u1ec1 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, n\u1ed7i oan c\u1ee7a Mesut Ozil m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u0169ng b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ozil-bi-duc-ruong-bo-da-co-tho-nhi-ky-lo-172-191936.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/ozil-bi-duc-ruong-bo-da-co-tho-nhi-ky-lo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ozil-bi-duc-ruong-bo-da-co-tho-nhi-ky-lo-172-191936.html\">Ozil b\u1ecb \u0110\u1ee9c ru\u1ed3ng b\u1ecf? \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 lo</span><br>\r\nSau nh\u1eefng scandal g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean ph\u1ed1 \u1edf qu\u00ea g\u1ed1c Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3, sau khi anh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mesut-ozil-cay-dang-bo-tuyen-that-bai-cua-ca-nen-bong-da-421-191850.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/Lothar-Matthaus-chi-trich-Mesut-Ozil-tham-te-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mesut-ozil-cay-dang-bo-tuyen-that-bai-cua-ca-nen-bong-da-421-191850.html\">Mesut Ozil cay \u0111\u1eafng b\u1ecf tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c: Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><br>\r\nC\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n n\u1ed5i \u0111\u00ecnh n\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1m ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ch\u1ea1nh l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1838","checkdouble":"192417"},{"date":"10:10 31/07","title":"\"T\u00e2n binh\" Man Utd tr\u1ea3i l\u00f2ng khi b\u1ecb Mourinho x\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00e1i k\u00e8o","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/tan-binh-man-utd-trai-long-khi-bi-mourinho-xep-da-trai-keo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Andreas Pereira kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n hoan ngh\u00eanh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ea7m tr\u1ecbch tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u00e0 chia b\u00e0i l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm d\u00e0nh cho m\u00ecnh sau khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Man Utd \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Andreas Pereira c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi qua nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Sau m\u1ed9t n\u0103m h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n \u1edf Valencia, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf v\u00e0 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sao tr\u1ebb Andreas Pereira n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1edbi \u1edf MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sao tr\u1ebb Andreas Pereira n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1edbi \u1edf MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/tan-binh-man-utd-trai-long-khi-bi-mourinho-xep-da-trai-keo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sao tr\u1ebb Andreas Pereira n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1edbi \u1edf MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Pereira c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng n\u00e9t t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00ecnh, anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;M\u1ed9t n\u0103m qua \u1edf Valencia v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi th\u00eam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u qu\u00fd b\u00e1u \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i \u0111\u1ecdc t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nhanh v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n h\u01a1n, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 m\u00ecnh h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea1m ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng l\u1ed7i l\u1ea7m c\u0169 n\u1eefa.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1ed1n d\u0129 mang s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 10 ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u00e1 c\u00e1nh, gi\u1edd Pereira \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Jose Mourinho s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7m tr\u1ecbch tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u00e0 chia b\u00e0i, m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00ednh anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n hoan ngh\u00eanh vai tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi m\u1ebb n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;HLV \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 t\u00f4i n\u00f3i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e2u \u00f4ng \u1ea5y y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 6 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eadn t\u1ee5y gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1. HLV h\u1eb3n \u0111\u00e3 nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf t\u00f4i m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Michael Carrick \u0111\u1ec1u s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean t\u00f4i trong m\u1ed7i bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, gi\u00fap t\u00f4i m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y l\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi ra th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u hay l\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-mu-truoc-mua-giai-201819-va-nu-cuoi-mim-cua-mourinho-172-192083.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/jose-mourinho-tuyen-bo-khong-mua-ve-xem-man-utd-thi-dau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-mu-truoc-mua-giai-201819-va-nu-cuoi-mim-cua-mourinho-172-192083.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: M.U kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng 4 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ec9m c\u1ee7a Mourinho</span><br>\r\nG\u1ea1t lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m v\u1edbi Milan sang m\u1ed9t b\u00ean, M.U kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9. M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1edd c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn. Tuy...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jose-mourinho-truoc-mua-giai-chet-boi-cam-bay-cua-chinh-minh-172-192305.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/jose-mourinho-truoc-mua-giai-chet-boi-cam-bay-cua-chinh-minh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jose-mourinho-truoc-mua-giai-chet-boi-cam-bay-cua-chinh-minh-172-192305.html\">Jose Mourinho tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i: Ch\u1ebft b\u1edfi c\u1ea1m b\u1eaby c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh?</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i, Jose Mourinho ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec7p kh\u00fac quen thu\u1ed9c xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. B\u1ea7u tr\u1eddi Man Utd tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u1ecb bao ph\u1ee7 b\u1edfi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1837","checkdouble":"192380"},{"date":"09:40 31/07","title":"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Golovin t\u1edbi Monaco","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-2-nguoi-that-bai-sau-thuong-vu-golovin-toi-monaco.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Golovin t\u1edbi Monaco thay v\u00ec Chelsea, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Michael Emenalo&nbsp;&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMichael Emenalo, c\u1ef1u gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u00e0 gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Monaco hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a Aleksandr Golovin t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi Golovin t\u1edbi Monaco h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi Golovin t\u1edbi Monaco h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-2-nguoi-that-bai-khi-Golovin-toi-Monaco-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Michael Emenalo gi\u00fap Monaco chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Golovin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh Emenalo l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng ra quy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga t\u1edbi Monaco, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ea1ch ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang ph\u00e2n v\u00e2n gi\u1eef nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn, ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Michael Emenalo khi\u1ebfn Golovin ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Monaco. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, song \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Monaco. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a Monaco ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Marina Granovskaia</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marina Granovskaia l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n b\u00e0 quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1c \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Chelsea ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Granovskaia d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ch\u01b0a l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marina Granovskaia dang khong lam tot cong viec cua minh\" title=\"Marina Granovskaia \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/ba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Marina Granovskaia \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea quan t\u00e2m Golovin tr\u01b0\u1edbc Monaco, song h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Marina Granovskaia \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Chelsea m\u1edbi chi ra 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 2 t\u00e2n binh, bao g\u1ed3m Jorginho v\u00e0 Robert Green. T\u00e2n HLV Sarri \u0111ang c\u1ea7n th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u HLV Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Rugani, Pjanic v\u00e0 Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus, song \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Marina Granovskaia v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o trong s\u1ed1 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 Chelsea h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Ruben Loftus-Cheek v\u00e0 Ross Barkley&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Maurizio Sarri th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 trong th\u1eddi gian d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Napoli, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1i Chelsea \u00f4ng c\u0169ng \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y. Jorginho v\u00e0 Kante l\u00e0 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a The Blues.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ross Barkley co co hoi da chinh khi Chelsea khong chieu mo thanh cong Golovin\" title=\"Ross Barkley c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh khi Chelsea kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Golovin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/bas.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ross Barkley c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh khi Chelsea kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Golovin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm Golovin \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5p v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111ang c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Golovin, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap Ruben Loftus-Cheek v\u00e0 Ross Barkley c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRuben Loftus-Cheek v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Crystal Palace theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, anh r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf Chelsea. Barkley c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Maurizio Sarri&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Chelsea ph\u1ea3i mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Golovin, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga. Song r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc BL\u0110 The Blues \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Maurizio Sarri da khong the co duoc Golovin trong doi hinh\" title=\"HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Golovin trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/sarri.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Golovin trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, HLV Sarri c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf cho s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Thibaut Courtois, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 38 tu\u1ed5i Robert Green.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u HLV Napoli \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Hazard, Willian hay Morata, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 m\u00e0 \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u01b0 Rugani hay Higuain \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, khi m\u00e0 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Sarri v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 m\u00e1y Chelsea tr\u01a1n tru \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: \u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia Nga</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Golovin l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nga. Ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bong da Nga huong loi khi Golovin toi Monaco\" title=\"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nga h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i khi Golovin t\u1edbi Monaco\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/nga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nga h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i khi Golovin t\u1edbi Monaco</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea, Golovin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. M\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGolovin t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t m\u00ecnh \u1edf Chelsea. Tuy nhi\u00ean, r\u1ea5t may \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-phap/chinh-thuc-monaco-chieu-mo-aleksandr-golovin-197-192165.html\" target=\"_blank\">Golovin \u0111\u1ebfn Monaco</span> thay v\u00ec t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Monaco, anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. HLV Jardim r\u1ea5t m\u00e1t tay v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, \u00f4ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Leonardo Jardim&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Leonardo Jardim \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. \u00d4ng bi\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, Monaco t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Leonardo Jardim lai co mot cau thu tiem nang de nhao nhan thanh sao lon\" title=\"Leonardo Jardim l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0o nh\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh sao l\u1edbn\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/hlv.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Leonardo Jardim l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0o nh\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh sao l\u1edbn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 thu h\u01a1n 400 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Kylian Mbappe, Fabinho, Thomas Lemar, Benjamin Mendy, Bernardo Silva v\u00e0 Tiemoue Bakayoko.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi Golovin h\u1ecd \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Leonardo Jardim l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i bi\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n Monaco ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn t\u1eeb Golovin trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n*Squawka</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1836","checkdouble":"192381"},{"date":"10:13 31/07","title":"HLV Leicester n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Maguire?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/hlv-leicester-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-mu-chieu-mo-maguire.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Spartak Trnava vs Legia Warsaw l\u00fac 01h30 ng\u00e0y 1/8 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1/Champions League 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Spartak Trnava vs Legia Warsaw 01h30 ng\u00e0y 18 c\u00fap C1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Spartak Trnava vs Legia Warsaw 01h30 ng\u00e0y 18 c\u00fap C1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Spartak_Trnava_vs_Legia_Warsaw.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Spartak Trnava vs Legia Warsaw</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Spartak Trnava vs Legia Warsaw: 2-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>\u1ede v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Legia Warszawa d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Cork City, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch CH Ireland, v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-0. Tuy v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 2, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Ba Lan khi h\u1ecd th\u00fac th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Spartak Trnava ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 0-2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLegia \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 r\u1eddi r\u1ea1c v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m. 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Ba Lan \u0111\u1ec3 thua t\u1edbi 3. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 h\u00e0nh trang t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Spartak Trnava h\u00f4m nay, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 h\u1ecd c\u00f2n g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf b\u1ecb d\u1eabn 2 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u00eda ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Spartak Trnava, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Slovakia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian v\u1eeba qua. 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t Spartak Trnava ch\u1ec9 thua 1 v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh t\u1edbi 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ca kh\u00fac kh\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n 9/13 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f3n kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, Legia Warszawa ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. Spartak Trnava do \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 thi tri\u1ec3n l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3i c\u00f4ng s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Tin v\u00e0o th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i ti\u1ebfp theo cho Spartak Trnava \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nSpartak Trnava: M. Chudy, M. Toth, M. Conka, I. Hladik, B. Godal, A. Kadlec, E. Grendel, J. Rada, L. Gressak, E. Jirka, M. Egho<br>\r\nLegia Warszawa: Skaba Brzyski, Dossa, Junior, Rzezniczak, Bereszynski, Furman, Jodlowiec, Kosecki, Helio Pinto, Kucharczyk, Dvalishvili</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1835","checkdouble":"192382"},{"date":"10:42 31/07","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1ea9u v\u1edbi t\u00e2n binh Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/huyen-thoai-mu-tiep-tuc-dau-khau-voi-tan-binh-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi b\u1ecb ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xherdan Shaqiri gay g\u1eaft \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Gary Neville quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 y\u00ean khi th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch s\u1eb7c m\u00f9i ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o \u0111\u00e0n em.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 13 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng r\u1ebb nh\u01b0 cho so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, vi\u1ec7c Xherdan Shaqiri t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u1eafc ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n s\u1edbm mu\u1ed9n sau khi Stoke City kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i Premier League.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Gary Neville ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Shaqiri c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Gary Neville ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Shaqiri c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/huyen-thoai-mu-tiep-tuc-dau-khau-voi-tan-binh-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Gary Neville ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Shaqiri c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ee9t \u00e1o ra \u0111i v\u00ec s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Shaqiri ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9, th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i anh v\u1eabn b\u1ecb <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/shaqiri-buong-loi-dap-tra-khi-bi-huyen-thoai-mu-chui-thang-mat-172-192056.html\" target=\"_blank\">anh em nh\u00e0 Neville ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p</span> v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng to\u00e0n t\u00e2m to\u00e0n \u00fd cho Stoke, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ra \u0111i cho d\u1ec5 khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 cho r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Man Utd ch\u1ec9 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng b\u1edbi m\u00f3c v\u1edb v\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ec3 \u201cd\u00ecm h\u00e0ng\u201d \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Liverpool, kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m v\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng l\u00e0m b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed5 th\u1eb9n v\u1edbi l\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e2m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 IC Cup 2018, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Man Utd \u0111\u1ebfn 4-1, v\u1edbi Shaqiri ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft. Nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00fa xe \u0111\u1ea1p ch\u1ed5ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Gary Neville c\u00e2m l\u1eb7ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng, c\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ra s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ed3m mi\u1ec7ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00e0n em thua k\u00e9m g\u1ea7n 20 tu\u1ed5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Shaqiri ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7n Ronaldinho th\u00ec m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1 hay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. C\u1eadu ta th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u01b0\u1eddi bi\u1ebfng, ch\u1ec9 th\u00edch \u0111\u1ee9ng y\u00ean m\u1ed9t ch\u1ed7 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u1edf ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng trong khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u0111ang b\u1ecb t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 th\u00edch Shaqiri, th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Xin ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu ta ra sao v\u00e0 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Stoke xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc.\u201d</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-liverpool-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-champions-league-172-192043.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/tan-binh-liverpool-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-champions-league.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-liverpool-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-champions-league-172-192043.html\">T\u00e2n binh Liverpool h\u1ea1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xherdan Shaqiri m\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n h\u1ea1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1834","checkdouble":"192383"},{"date":"10:24 31/07","title":"HLV HAGL tin t\u01b0\u1edfng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-hagl-tin-tuong-hoc-tro-se-tao-nen-su-khac-biet-tai-olympic-viet-nam.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV HAGL \u00f4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</h2><h2>HLV HAGL tin h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV HAGL tin h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV HAGL tin h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n 8 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i V-League.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n HAGL D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch l\u0169y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa, \u0111a s\u1ed1 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, cho n\u00ean t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd \u1ed5n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u00f4i, \u1edf l\u1ee9a tu\u1ed5i U23, c\u00e1c HAGL s\u1ebd c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 HAGL n\u00f3i ri\u00eang. Ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 khung t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho ASIAD 18. Suy cho c\u00f9ng c\u00e1i \u0111\u00edch m\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c thay v\u00ec m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t\u201d, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng HAGL chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o Bongdaplus.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat lo ng\u1ea1i khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t sau khi g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb v\u1eaft ki\u1ec7t s\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i V-League.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat lo l\u1eafng l\u00e0 m\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 d\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a HAGL kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. C\u0169ng n\u00ean nh\u1edb tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, V-League ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u li\u00ean t\u1ee5c trung b\u00ecnh 1 tu\u1ea7n kho\u1ea3ng 2 tr\u1eadn trong th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra World Cup 2018\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh sau nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n v\u1ea5p ng\u00e3 t\u1ea1i V-League, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL s\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/duoc-thay-park-ngoi-khen-thu-mon-dang-van-lam-sang-cua-bat-chinh-168-192379.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/duoc-thay-park-ngoi-khen-thu-mon-dang-van-lam-sang-cua-bat-chinh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/duoc-thay-park-ngoi-khen-thu-mon-dang-van-lam-sang-cua-bat-chinh-168-192379.html\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park ng\u1ee3i khen, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh</span><br>\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1833","checkdouble":"192384"}]}